author: NEW YORK DAILY NEWS
title: Comedian makes fun of healthy eating habits on Instagram
text:
deliciouslystella/via Instagram Deliciouslystella parody instagram account This stand-up comedian is shaming everyone’s healthy eating habits online — one spoonful of chocolate peanut butter at a time.
Bella Younger, of London, regularly posts on her parody Instagram account, DeliciouslyStella , to showcase beers for breakfast and eating Reese’s peanut butter chocolate spread straight out of the jar.
“I went on Instagram and everyone seemed to be doing yoga on a beach or eating vegetables masquerading as desserts,” she told the Daily News in an email.
